items.name: Efficiency Nodes for ComfyUI
items.description:
A collection of ComfyUI custom nodes to help streamline workflows and reduce total node count.


Github Repo: https://github.com/LucianoCirino/efficiency-nodes-comfyui


Currently Available Nodes:

Ksampler (Efficient)

  • A modded KSampler with the ability to preview/output images and run scripts.

Efficient Loader

  • A combination of common initialization nodes.

XY Plotter Nodes

  • A collection of nodes that allows users to specify parameters for the KSampler (Efficient) to plot on a grid.

Image Overlay

  • Node that allows for flexible image overlaying.

SimpleEval Nodes

  • A collection of nodes that allows users to write simple Python expressions for a variety of data types using the "simpleeval" library.

modelVersions.name: v1.92
modelVersions.description:
# UPDATES/CHANGES:

1. Support for basic SDXL workflows via the new Eff. Loader SDXL and KSampler SDXL (Eff.) nodes.

2. Complete redesign of many nodes, from the XY Inputs, to the Stacker nodes.

3. Tons of new features, from enhanced seed control on all KSamplers to many new XY Plot input types.

4. New HiResFix Script node that allows for ez latent upscaling.

and SO MUCH MORE...

modelVersions.name: v1.72
modelVersions.description:
UPDATES/CHANGES:

  • Added Control Net support to the 'Efficient Loader' and 'XY Plot' nodes via the new 'Control Net Stacker' node.

  • 4 NEW XY Plot input nodes. 'Add/Return Noise', 'Start at Step', 'End at Step', and 'Control Net Strenghts'.

  • New KSampler Adv. (Efficient) node.

  • The "preview_image" input from the Efficient KSampler's has been deprecated, its been replaced by inputs "preview_method" & "vae_decode".
    The new Efficient KSampler's "preview_method" input temporarily overrides the global preview setting set by the ComfyUI manager.

  • Several XY Plot input nodes have been revamped for better XY Plot setup efficiency.

Extras:

  • Enable hot-reload of XY Plot lora, checkpoint, sampler, scheduler, vae via the ComfyUI refresh button.

  • Upgraded the auto installation of required packages from requirements.txt.

modelVersions.name: v1.62
modelVersions.description:
Efficiency Nodes v1.62 Updates

UPDATES/CHANGES:

  • LoRA stacking is now supported for the 'Efficienct Loader' and XY Plot via the 'LoRA Stacker' node.

  • Massive code refactoring done to accomodate the new LoRA stacking changes.

BUG FIXES:

  • Fixed a bug where the XY Plot would not display the correct results when one XY type was "Sampler" and the other "Scheduler".

  • Fixed issues with XY Plot printouts.

FOR PEOPLE HAVING ERRORS:

  • The 'Efficient Loader' node's outputs have been changed. This means 'Efficient Loaders' in existing workflows must be manually replaced with a new ones from your node library.

modelVersions.name: v1.57
modelVersions.description:
***Efficiency Nodes v1.57 Updates***

# UPDATES/CHANGES:

- 4 new XY Plot Input nodes HAVE BEEN ADDED: "Positive Prompt S/R", "Negative Prompt S/R",

"Clip Skip", and "Manual XY Entry".

- Renamed the 'Join XY Inputs' node to 'Join XY Inputs of Same Type' to aliviate confusion.

- Efficient Loader LoRAs now get applied also to "Checkpoint" XY Plots.

- 'cache_settings.json' has been renamed 'node_settings.json'.

- Added a few new customizable node options on the 'node_settings.json'.

# BUG FIXES:

- Fixed a bug where the Efficient Loader would not clear its models cache properly, causing

it to repeatedly load models (ckpt/vae/lora) after any changes.

- Cleaned and fixed XY Plot console printouts.

- Fixed text clipping issues with the XY Plot's Y_labels.

- Fixed a bug where the XY Plot Image results did not always visibly align with the

KSampler (Efficient) IMAGE/LATENT outputs.

个人感觉八宝备老师画风前后期差异挺大，我选择的是偏后期的画风。

我使用anythingv4.5,权重0.5-0.9。最好使用Hires. Fix。

我顺便做了一下几个主要角色，你可以使用Happoubi Jin+角色名召唤她们。

可以召唤的角色有：蓮華Tsukioka Karen，燈露椎Dorothy，亜璃子Alice，篝ノ霧枝Kagarino Kirie，稲森はるInamori Haru，沢渡雫Sawatari Shizuku。其中Dorothy需要结合short hair使用，其他的使用名字即可。召唤角色时候推荐权重0.7-0.9。

I feel that there is a significant difference in the before and after style of Happoubi Jin's artwork, and I chose the processing style.

I used anythingv4.5, with a weight of 0.5-0.9. It is recommended to use Hires. Fix.

Trigger words: Happoubi Jin, which can trigger the art style.

I also made several main characters, and you can summon them using Happoubi Jin + character name. The characters that can be summoned are: Tsukioka Karen, Dorothy, Alice, Kagarino Kirie, Inamori Haru, and Sawatari Shizuku. Dorothy needs to be used with "short hair" to summon, while the others can be summoned using their names. It is recommended to use a weight of 0.7-0.9 when summoning characters.

items.name: Rurutiaza_血族Bloodline：露露缇雅
items.description:
角色为由漫画家爱欧创作的国漫《血族：bloodline》系列中的重要角色露露缇雅。

因为素材均为漫画内容且数量有限，所以不可避免的在生成时相对较易产生水印或文字内容，另外值得一提的是也时常会生成多余的耳朵，推荐添加“text“”watermark”“extra ears”等负面提示词和正面提示词“pointy ears”以控制生成图片的质量。

模型质量有待通过更清晰的图源和更精细的抠图提升。

漫画原作者爱发电：https://afdian.net/a/iomanga

如果你有闲钱，可以通过以上链接去支持一下原作者。

The character is an important character in the Chinese animation series "血族：bloodline" created by the comic artist 爱欧, and her name is Rurutiaza.

Due to the limited source material being exclusively from the comic, it is inevitable for watermarks or textual elements to occasionally appear in the generated outputs. Additionally, it's worth noting that the model may generate extra ears, so it's recommended to add negative prompts such as "text", "watermark", and "extra ears", as well as positive prompts like "pointy ears", to control the quality of the generated images.

The quality of the model could be further improved with clearer image sources and more meticulous cropping.

items.name: BreezeMix-Realistic
items.description:
介绍

这个模型源于我个人经常使用的lora和ckpt的融合，介于2.5D和3D之间，个人审美偏好的结果。以下是模型的混合公式：

 

0.9(0.75(LuckyStrikeMixv0.1)+0.25(chilloutmix_Ni-fp16)+(koreanDollLikeness_v15:0.2,shojovibe_v11:0.3,fashionGirl_v45:0.4,LoraKAigirlFace_kAigirlFace2:0.5,eyeLora_eyesV10:0.6:OUTD))+0.1(chilloutmix_Ni-fp16)

 

这个融合的过程中在2.5D和3D之间摇摆不定，最终效果只是我个人的选择。VAE 已在此模型中烘焙，因此无需加载任何额外的 VAE。感谢以上作者提供的优秀模型。 顺便一提，所有的预览图像都是使用这个模型生成的，没有使用额外 LORA。

 

 

Introduce

This model is derived from the fusion of lora and ckpt that I personally often use, between 2.5D and 3D, the result of personal aesthetic preference. Here is the blending formula for the model:

 

0.9(0.75(LuckyStrikeMixv0.1)+0.25(chilloutmix_Ni-fp16)+(koreanDollLikeness_v15:0.2,shojovibe_v11:0.3,fashionGirl_v45:0.4,LoraKAigirlFace_kAigirlFace2:0.5,eyeLora_eyesV10:0.6:OUTD))+0.1(chilloutmix_Ni-fp16)

 

In the process of fusion, I wavered between 2.5D and 3D, and the final effect is just my personal choice. VAE are already baked into this model, so there is no need to load any additional VAE. Thanks to the above authors for their excellent models. By the way, all preview images are generated using this model without any extra LORA.

I've tested it with song lyrics, massive wildcard prompts, styles, booru tags, and i've only hit a few walls yet. How far can you take it?

WARNINGS:

  1. This model is VERY thirsty, and will steer towards NSFW if you let it.

  2. This model does not do wel at low steps

  3. Some things require thinking outside the box, it's based on a generic model, so go ham on crazy ideas.

  4. Use prompt editing for the best results!

  5. I suck at upscaling images, but this model does pretty well using large initial generations

Default negative prompt:

low quality, lowres, error, fault, crude, blurry, undefined, jagged, spiky, ugly hands, extra arm, extra hand, split arm, missing finger, extra finger, three fingers, four fingers, six fingers, disfigured, unclear, indistinct, merged fingers, bad anatomy, misplaced hand, misplaced foot, sex, nsfw, leotard, slutty, signature, watermark, text, artist, distorted, sex, nsfw, leotard, slutty,

items.name: IronCatLoRA #3 - Anime vibrancy & simplifier Style
items.description:
IronCatLoRA #3 - Anime vibrancy & simplifier Style

Making LoRA's is a thing I do for fun. So if you like what I do? You can help me out by just using the LoRA and leaving a review!

Want more vibrant colours, less detailed textures and more defined line art? Then you came to the right place, let me vibrance you up! This LoRA is an anime style LoRA, meaning you can just apply this LoRA to any anime based checkpoint. The style that is applied will make your image have more vibrant colours, it will make details/textures less detailed for a more anime look and it will accentuate the line art. Perhaps you have an anime checkpoint that you really like how it handles generation, but you also really like a more simple anime look. If that's the case, than perhaps this LoRA will suit your taste!

I've created this anime style LoRA because I like simple, vibrant and noticeable line art style based anime art/images. I've offset the LoRA weight so it's in my mind at the perfect weight where it will do its intended job as by my vision. This means you can use the LoRA at the default weight of 1.0and you're totally fine! There's no trigger word needed, all you need to do is to use the LoRA as is. But you can of course lower the weight, if you want less of the style applied.

In order to make it easy for you to see what the actual style changes, I've uploaded multiple image grids, that display multiple checkpoint and multiple concepts. This should hopefully give you an idea what the style on average will look like. It will of course depend on what checkpoint you use, so be sure to check the image grids out to get an idea. The columns that have no text above them, is the generation result from the checkpoint without this LoRA applied.

p.s. my current favourite checkpoint to combine this LoRA with is YesMix. The first image on the carousel which is also used for the cards when browsing models, is created with it.

items.name: 晖映 Enhanced Backlighting
items.description:
晖映 Enhanced Backlighting

[Eng ver below]

607323927751959196

这是一个用来改善逆光侧光环境光照效果的Lora，许多模型的noise_offset未经调整，会导致画面整体亮度过于均衡，显得没有暗区重点或者摄影反光效果，尤其是二次元类model，即使是给出了backlighting的prompt，人物依然会显得亮度和环境保持一致，缺乏重点的突出，显得画面色调很”平“，这个LORA特意加深了对比度来改善这个问题，对于二三次元的模型都有自然光的照射改善效果。

  • 特别提示：由于trigger word忘记区分，使用backlighting这个prompt会比较重的加深对比和自然光效，如果你不喜欢这种风格，可以尝试去掉它并改变Lora的权重，可以得到一些较轻的效果。计划在后续版本里通过特殊关键字解决这个问题。

  • 特别提示2：这个Lora针对丁达尔现象也有不错的效果，甚至可以在二次元模型中搭配另外一个尚在完善中的Lora模拟出来。即Komorebi 日语(木漏れ日)，效果请见例图。待测试完善后会择机发布的。

  • 特别提示3：Lora的权重和CFG高低都会影响阳光的效果，如果不希望画面出现太多夕阳余晖的感觉，可以通过提示词改善或者降低权重或CFG

对比效果如下：

提示词均为1girl,backlighting

Enhanced Backlighting is a Lora used to improve the backlighting and sidelighting effects in environments with strong lighting contrast. Many models have not adjusted their noise_offset, which can result in an overly balanced overall brightness and a lack of emphasis on dark areas or photographic reflection effects, especially for 2D models. Even when the prompt for backlighting is given, the character still appears to have the same brightness as the environment, lacking a prominent highlight and making the image appear very "flat" in tone. This LORA intentionally deepens the contrast to improve this problem and has a natural light illumination improvement effect for both 2D and 3D models.

  • Special Note: Due to forgetting to distinguish the trigger word, using the prompt 'backlighting' will heavily increase the contrast and natural light effect. If you don't like this style, you can try removing it and changing the weight of Lora to achieve a lighter effect. We plan to solve this problem through special keywords in future versions.

  • Special Note 2: This Lora has a good effect on the Ding Darr phenomenon, and can even be combined with another Lora, which is still under development, to simulate the effect of 'Komorebi' in Japanese (sunlight filtering through trees) for 2D models. Please refer to the example image for the effect. It will be released after testing and improvement.

  • Special Note 3: The weight and CFG of Lora will affect the effect of sunshine. If you don't want the screen to have too much sunset glow, you can improve or lower the weight or CFG through prompt words.

The comparison effect is as upside img.

The prompt words are '1girl' and 'backlighting'.
